snippet.title: Swordship - Official Gameplay Trailer | gamescom 2022
snippet.description:
In Swordship, you'll need to master the art of dodging obstacles and enemies at breakneck speeds while using their own weapons against them. 

Swordship releases December 2022 for PlayStation, Xbox, PC, and Nintendo Switch.
